Package: BayesianPriorsTool
Title: Tools for Prior Elicitation in Bayesian Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Arthur", "M. Albuquerque", email = "arthur_albuquerque1@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Arthur M. Albuquerque <arthur_albuquerque1@yahoo.com>
Description: Provides functions to compute standard deviations and
    generate plots for weakly informative priors in Bayesian
    random-effects meta-analysis models, aiding prior elicitation
    for the overall effect parameter (mu).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    stats
URL: https://github.com/arthur-albuquerque/BayesianPriorsTool
BugReports: https://github.com/arthur-albuquerque/BayesianPriorsTool/issues
